<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?><Section Number="0030.06" xmlns="http://StatRev.xsd"><Catchline xml:space="preserve">Liability of sureties.</Catchline><SectionBody><Text xml:space="preserve" Style="Intro">The sureties, if any, are liable for all fines and amercements imposed upon the principal, or sheriff.</Text></SectionBody><History xml:space="preserve">s. 4, ch. 987, 1859; RS 1240; GS 1669; RGS 2874; CGL 4571; s. 1, ch. 20719, 1941; s. 12, ch. 98-34.</History></Section>